        {
            "id": "tradingview:eeba11b4182dd:0",
            "title": "Southside Bancshares Inc Q2 2026: Revenue $103.9M, Net income $26.84M, EPS $0.9— 10-Q Summary",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Southside Bancshares Inc reported second-quarter 2026 results with revenue of $103.9M, net income of $26.84M and diluted EPS of $0.9, each up versus the year-ago quarter as the company shifted funding sources and expanded fee-based businesses.</span></p><p class=\"\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Financial Highlights</span></strong></p><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Revenue: Total interest and dividend income $103.9M for Q2 2026 vs $98.6M in year-ago quarter (5.4% YoY).</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Net income: $26.84M for Q2 2026 vs $21.81M in the year-ago quarter (23.0% YoY).</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Diluted EPS: $0.90 for Q2 2026 vs $0.72 in the year-ago quarter (25.0% YoY).</span></li></ul><p class=\"\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Business Highlights</span></strong></p><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Revenue momentum: Net interest income and other improvements drove year-over-year net income and EPS growth for the quarter.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Deposit &amp; funding shift: The company moved from brokered deposits toward wholesale funding via FHLB and FRDW, changing its funding mix and liquidity channels.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Revenue diversification: Noninterest income rose, supported by trust fees, BOLI, brokerage and swap/mortgage-related fees, reducing reliance on loan interest.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Operational expansion: Southside opened new branches in Tyler (Bellwood Park) and The Woodlands to bolster market presence and origination capacity.</span></li></ul><p class=\"\"><span>Original SEC Filing: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec icon-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/705432/000070543226000105/sbsi-20260630.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">SOUTHSIDE BANCSHARES INC [ SBSI ] - 10-Q - Jul. 24, 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-powered summary. It may contain inaccuracies. Consider verifying important information with the source. Please note this summary is solely based on documents filed with the SEC.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:eeba11b4182dd:0-southside-bancshares-inc-q2-2026-revenue-103-9m-net-income-26-84m-eps-0-9-10-q-summary/",
